66
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,360
try it on.

67
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:43,760
Do you like it?

68
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,000
Hmm.

69
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,120
This one is really nice.

70
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:56,800
Sir, I'll take it.

71
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,600
But,

72
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,200
