76
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,120
First come, first serve.

77
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:07,360
Besides,

78
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:08,360
The Rose,

79
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,880
