80
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,200
Anyone else wearing it

81
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,440
just wouldn't be fitting,

82
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,120
right?

83
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,000
Sir,

84
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,240
fill in any amount you like.

85
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:21,840
Sir Shen,

86
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,040
it's very kind of you.

87
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:24,800
Zhiwei,

88
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,360
