99
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,640
Yunzheng, you've finally come around.

100
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,040
I'll go tell dad right away.

101
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,760
As soon as I told him,

102
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:22,200
he agreed immediately.

103
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:24,000
So from now on,

104
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:25,160
Yunzheng

105
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:27,000
will be your brother-in-law.

106
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,240
Moli,

107
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:32,760
