108
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,160
Are you that impatient?

109
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,560
Of course.

110
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:39,160
This was your idea.

111
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:52,640
Alright then,

112
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:54,920
